<%= javascript_include_tag "dates" %>
<h1><span>&lt;</span>web labs<span>/&gt;</span></h1>
<article class="text">
  This is a simple site I will use for cool experiments with web technologies. Anything cool I find on the web
  or make myself I put here. Most of the things here will be expanded on one day when I find some time.
</article>
<article class="text">
  This website uses middleman for static site generation, so everything should be pretty fast and the website should
  work without javascript
</article>
<hr>
<h2>Experiments</h2>
<% sitemap.resources
  .select { |resource| resource.path =~ /^experiments\// }
  .sort_by {|obj| obj.data.date}
  .reverse()
  .each do |resource|
%>
  <% link_to resource.path do %><article class="link">
    <h3><%= resource.data.title %></h3>
    <div class="date local-date"><%= DateTime.parse(resource.data.date) %></div>
    <p><%= resource.data.description || "" %></p>
  </article><% end %>
<% end %>